       01 RESP-QZERO        PIC S9(8) VALUE 23.
       01 DFHRESP-QZERO     PIC S9(8) VALUE 23.
       01 RESP-SIGNAL       PIC S9(8) VALUE 24.
       01 DFHRESP-SIGNAL    PIC S9(8) VALUE 24.
       01 RESP-QBUSY        PIC S9(8) VALUE 25.
       01 DFHRESP-QBUSY     PIC S9(8) VALUE 25.
